author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents TRAVO performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 06, 2024. 

Songs:
00:09  Sleeper
07:15  Arrow Of Motion
15:52  Faceless Ghoul
22:39  Turn To The Sun

Gonçalo Ferreira - Guitar, Vocals

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
